description: DevOps rules — Docker, CI/CD, deployment, environments, monitoring
globs: Dockerfile*,.github/**/*,.dockerignore

## DevOps Rules
1. Dockerfile for production multi-stage build
2. CI/CD via GitHub Actions
3. Environment variables via .env files (not committed)
4. Health check endpoint: GET /api/health
5. Build before deploy: pnpm build passes
6. Test before deploy: pnpm test passes
7. Production: minified, tree-shaken, gzip compressed
